        "definition": "Common collocations with \"time\"",
        "examples": [
          "Pass the time — Do something to occupy oneself while waiting",
          "Spend time — Use time for a specific activity",
          "Take time — Require a significant amount of time",
          "Fly on time — Depart or arrive as scheduled (flight)",
          "By the time — When a particular moment arrives",
          "Part-time — Working or studying for fewer hours than full-time",
          "Full-time — Working or studying for the entire standard period"
        ]
      }
